high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the spatula off of the counter.
Walk over to the sink on you right.
Put the spatula in the sink and turn on the faucet, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean spatula.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then hang a right and walk up to the round wooden table in the corner of the room.
Put the clean spatula on the round wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on a round wooden table.

high_descs: Turn right and move forward, then turn left to face the counter with the microwave.
Pick up the spatula from the counter.
Turn around and walk toward the table, then turn left to go to the sink.
Wash the spatula in the sink.
Turn right and go forward, then turn right and go to the round table ahead of you.
Put the spatula on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the round table.

high_descs: Pick up the spatula to the right of the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Rinse the spatula in the sink.
Turn around and veer left to the wooden table.
Place the spatula on the table in front of the perfume bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spatula on a table.
